Package topquizbackend

This package contains all the Back-End classes/objects for use in the topquiz package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackEndTester
    This is just a class for testing the Back-End classes.
    GenerateQuestionBank
    This class is used to generate all the Questions used in the final-product of this application.
    InteractiveQuestion
    The InteractiveQuestion class contains the back-end IA Question data and the methods needed in the back-end for the proper execution of front-end methods.
    MultipleChoiceQuestion
    The MultipleChoieQuestion class contains the back-end MC Question data and the methods needed in the back-end for the proper execution of front-end methods.
    Question
    Parent Class to all the other ___Question classes.
    QuestionBank
    The QuestionBank class is used by the front-end classes and packages as a means of accessing many of the objects detailed in the topquizbackend package.
    ShortAnswerQuestion
    The ShortAnswerQuestion class contains the back-end SA Question data and the methods needed in the back-end for the proper execution of front-end methods.

Package topquizbackend Description

This package contains all the Back-End classes/objects for use in the topquiz package. The vast-majority of Back-End methods, objects and data members may be found and accessed through this package.
